    "description": "Photo album markers configuration. To add a new location or photo, simply add an entry following the examples below.",
    
    "_instructions": [
        "HOW TO ADD A NEW PHOTO TO AN EXISTING LOCATION:",
        "  1. Place your image file in the public/images/ folder",
        "  2. Find the location id in the 'markers' array below",
        "  3. Add a new entry to that location's 'images' array with 'path' and 'caption'",
        "",
        "HOW TO ADD A NEW LOCATION:",
        "  1. Copy one of the existing marker objects in the 'markers' array",
        "  2. Update lat, lng, name, caption, and images",
        "  3. You can find lat/lng coordinates at https://www.latlong.net/",
        "",
        "TIP: Image paths are relative to the public/ folder.",
        "     Example: 'images/paris_1.jpg' means the file is at public/images/paris_1.jpg"
    ],

